snippet.title: Best VGM 2367 - Croc : Legend of the Gobbos - Snow Island 3
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PS1 / Saturn / PC
Croc : Legend of the Gobbos (1997)
Snow Island 3
Justin Scharvona

Twitter: https://twitter.com/SupraDarky
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SupraDarky
